表的代码预览支付

drop index Payments_PK on Payments;


alter table Payments
drop foreign key "FK_PAYMENTS_贷款-支付_LOANS";

drop table if exists Payments;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: Payments */
/*==============================================================*/
create table Payments
(
loan_id varchar(60) not null comment '',
payment_id varchar(60) not null comment '',
payment_amount float(8,2) comment '',
payment_date date comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Payments_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index Payments_PK on Payments
(
payment_id
);

alter table Payments add constraint "FK_PAYMENTS_贷款-支付_LOANS" foreign key (loan_id)
references loans (loan_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
